The paper discusses the emerging landscape of DLT-based identity management, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and cybersecurity (cs.CY). The paper also evaluates three representative proposals, which involves database systems (cs.DB), distributed computing (cs.DC), and software engineering (cs.SE).
